OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,FAn economic opportunity of more than
OL,8,F#900 million in England is being
OL,9,F"missed" by property transactions
OL,10,Ffalling through, calculations by
OL,11,FRightmove suggest.
OL,13,FThe calculation is based on the volume
OL,14,Fof property transactions falling
OL,15,Fthrough and not returning to market
OL,16,Fwithin a year, factoring in typical
OL,17,Fstamp duty and estate agency
OL,18,Fcommission.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@HO]
