OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,FRightmove estimated that nearly #392
OL,8,Fmillion in potential estate agency
OL,9,Frevenue and #515 million in potential
OL,10,Fstamp duty were lost last year to fall
OL,11,Fthroughs that did not come back to
OL,12,Fmarket.
OL,14,FSeparately, it estimated there is a
OL,15,Fnearly #7 million economic opportunity
OL,16,Ffor Scotland, and an opportunity of
OL,17,Faround #23 million in Wales by
OL,18,Freducing lost sales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
