OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,FThe separate calculations consider the
OL,8,Flower rate of fall throughs in
OL,9,FScotland, and the differing land taxes
OL,10,Fin Scotland and Wales.
OL,12,FLast year, it took an average of five
OL,13,Fmonths for a house purchase across
OL,14,FBritain to go through the completion
OL,15,Fprocess, Rightmove said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
