OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772179261
OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,FRightmove's data indicates that 6% of
OL,8,Fproperty transactions fall through and
OL,9,Fdo not come back to market within 12
OL,10,Fmonths, while around a fifth (23%) of
OL,11,Ftransactions initially fall through
OL,12,Fbefore later completing successfully.
OL,14,FJohan Svanstrom, Rightmove's CEO,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Our analysis highlights the
OL,16,Fscale of the economic opportunity if
OL,17,Ffall through rates can be reduced.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
