OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772179261
OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,F"More than one in five transactions
OL,8,Fare affected by fall throughs, costing
OL,9,Fagents either lost or delayed fees and
OL,10,Fleading to some home movers paying
OL,11,Fthousands in repeat costs."
OL,13,FRightmove used HM Revenue and Customs
OL,14,F(HMRC) house sales figures and its
OL,15,Faverage transaction price data to make
OL,16,Fits estimates for the amount of money
OL,17,Fbeing lost. It also took into account
OL,18,Ftransactions where stamp duty relief
OL,19,Ffor first-time buyers may have been
OL,20,Fapplied.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@[O]
