OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,FCraig Webster, managing director at
OL,8,FTiger Estates in Blackpool said: "The
OL,9,Ftrue cost of those collapsed
OL,10,Ftransactions goes far beyond a single
OL,11,Flost fee.
OL,13,F"When a sale falls through, the agent
OL,14,Fhas already invested substantial time
OL,15,Fand cost in securing the listing,
OL,16,Fmarketing the property, vetting and
OL,17,Fmanaging buyers, and progressing the
OL,18,Fsale through to and beyond offer stage.
OL,26,@pD@bOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
