CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772179261
OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,F"Anything that improves transaction
OL,8,Fefficiency ` particularly in
OL,9,Fconveyancing and data flows between
OL,10,Fparties ` will reduce the risk of fall
OL,11,Fthroughs.
OL,13,F"Faster, clearer communication between
OL,14,Fagents, lenders, solicitors and buyers
OL,15,Fbuilds confidence throughout the chain
OL,16,Fand helps prevent delays from
OL,17,Fsnowballing into cancellations.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
