OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,FMary-Lou Press, NAEA (National
OL,8,FAssociation of Estate Agents)
OL,9,FPropertymark president, said: "While
OL,10,Ffall throughs can never be eliminated
OL,11,Fentirely, many are preventable with
OL,12,Fbetter upfront information, improved
OL,13,Fcommunication between parties, and a
OL,14,Fmore streamlined and digitised
OL,15,Ftransaction system.
OL,17,F"Our member agents work tirelessly to
OL,18,Fhold chains together and guide
OL,19,Fconsumers through what is often a
OL,20,Fcomplex and stressful process."
OL,26,@qD@_OUyD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
