OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,FShe added: "We support measures that
OL,8,Fpromote greater digitisation, earlier
OL,9,Fprovision of material information, and
OL,10,Fstronger collaboration across the
OL,11,Fsector.
OL,13,F"However, reform must work for
OL,14,Fconsumers and practitioners alike,
OL,15,Fensuring the system is both efficient
OL,16,Fand robust."
OL,18,FAneisha Beveridge, research director
OL,19,Fat Hamptons and Connells Group, said:
OL,20,F"Some types of sales are particularly
OL,21,Ffragile in this environment.
OL,26,@oD@LOUuD@AOUxD@LO]|D@AOU
