OL,3,C#900m economic opportunity in England
OL,4,C'lost to property sales falling
OL,5,Cthrough'
OL,7,F"Flats tend to be more prone to
OL,8,Fdelays, often because issues uncovered
OL,9,Fin leasehold packs or building
OL,10,Fpaperwork take longer to resolve.
OL,12,F"Chain-based sales are also more
OL,13,Fexposed, with a single setback
OL,14,Freverberating through multiple linked
OL,15,Ftransactions.
OL,17,F"Ultimately, the later a sale breaks
OL,18,Fdown, the greater the financial and
OL,19,Femotional cost."
